org.conqat.lib.commons.region

Class SimpleRegion

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.conqat.lib.commons.region.SimpleRegion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<SimpleRegion>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LineBasedRegion, OffsetBasedRegion, Region

    public class SimpleRegion
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<SimpleRegion>, java.io.Serializable
    A simple region with only start and end. If you also need a description string (origin), use Region. Both start and end positions are inclusive.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
